name: MY FAE
description:
Poison is what kept you going,
Hatred with beauty
Disgust with your body
And lust for jealousy. 

Once you saw yourself in the mirror
Suddenly I saw a crack on your poisoned skull
Then I started to question your reality;
"Why do you fill your head with such lies?"

Years went by and your finally free. 
The tiny crack became a start
Of how you started to see your worth. 
Now roses fill your void.
